| **Artifact ID**   | `TOOL-ANALYZE-DOCS-COMPLIANCE-001` | The Sovereign ID. |
| **Official Name** | `analyze_docs_compliance.py`   | The Filename.     |
| **Version**       | **v15.0 [OMEGA]**              | The Standard.     |
| **Domain**        | `GVRN`                         | The Subject.      |
